<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your SQUADZ Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #333333;
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 22px;
    }
    .content p {
      color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .otp-box {
      background-color: #fff5f5;
      border: 2px dashed #f5576c;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #f5576c;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    }
    .expiry-notice {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .expiry-notice p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #856404;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .security-notice {
      background-color: #f8d7da;
      border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .security-notice p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #721c24;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .security-notice strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #777777;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üîê Password Reset</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
      <p>We received a request to reset your SQUADZ account password. Use the verification code below to proceed with resetting your password:</p>
      
      <div class="otp-box">
        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">Your Reset Code</p>
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
      </div>

      <div class="expiry-notice">
        <p>‚è±Ô∏è This code expires in <strong>{{expiryMinutes}} minutes</strong>. After entering the code, you'll have 15 minutes to complete your password reset.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="security-notice">
        <p><strong>üõ°Ô∏è Security Notice</strong></p>
        <p>If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email and ensure your account is secure. Your password won't change unless you complete the reset process.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 10px;">If you're concerned about your account security, please contact us at <strong>{{supportEmail}}</strong></p>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 25px; font-size: 13px; color: #777;">This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>SQUADZ</strong> - FC25 Pro Clubs Tournament Management</p>
      <p>¬© 2025 SQUADZ. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

